SKILLREQUEST: Request a secondary OCC skill

Syntax: skillrequest
        skillrequest <number>
        skillrequest cancel

DESCRIPTION:
  Request an additional skill from your OCC skill categories. A wizard must
  approve the request before the skill is granted.

  skillrequest
      Show a numbered list of skills you do not yet have.

  skillrequest <number>
      Submit a request for the numbered skill from the latest list.

  skillrequest cancel
      Cancel your pending request.

NOTES:
  You must have an OCC set. Only skills valid for your OCC categories appear.
  Online wizards are notified when you submit or cancel a request.

SEE ALSO: skills, abilities, score
